# Phase 3: Attachments System

## Context Links
- Phase 1 (dependency): [phase-01-postgres-prisma-migration.md](phase-01-postgres-prisma-migration.md)
- Phase 2 (dependency): [phase-02-s3-file-storage.md](phase-02-s3-file-storage.md)
